 ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(16,16,'TS: n/a',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(17,17,'\"DG: Increase the coverage and market transparency via the EM IIB sales. Improve hit-rate by closer cooperation with regional companies. Reach and execute cooperation agreement with LCB IND, UAE,BEL,POR,COL,SEA, leverage advantages of both sides, and optimize business model (incl. tax, customs, logistics). Keep strategic partnership with key EPCs.Establish local R&D, PLM, Logistic, Quality Control competencies for Meter and HES export.\"',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(18,18,'MS: Evaluated as no Opp. for MS. (pls. refer to R_2012_CHN_051)',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(19,19,'LP: Continuous efforts in the localization of power distribution product portfolio in SEAL (e.g. 3VA launched in FY15 with local delivery starting June 2016); R&D CoC in SCPS; full WA PLM.',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(20,20,'TR: Aleady Set up R&D center of DT',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(21,21,'HP:medium Opp. Measures:- 800kV Bushing & 1100kV LT CB localization in progress; Further localiaion initiatives in clarification or development',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(22,22,'TS: PTL localization to traget on Grid / City market',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(23,23,'DG:Already considered in FY17 BTA stretched target.',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(24,24,'MS: Evaluated as no Opp. beyond EM2020 growth plan. ',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(25,25,'LP: Identify key verticals matching  5 year plan to speed go to market. Opportunity for LP in leveraging PU & O EPC sales team for white spots in PSB and O EPC',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(26,26,'TR: Focus on upcoming UHV projects esp. in 2015-21- Localization of HVDC design. - DT R&D center set up',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:29','2018-10-09 17:47:29'),(27,27,'H