cooperation in DG business; SPERI is working on 501K packaging design.3)complete.3 sets RB211 for MD booked ','2018-10-09 17:47:30','2018-10-09 17:47:30'),(32,32,'Extend the market share via possibilities study, 1) Speed up the cooperation with CNPE/CNCS for nuclear business  2). Working together with FSP and HTC for SGT-800 TCS localization. 3). CSP control system and LoC system approach.','Ongoing measure.1).  the consensus is reached by HQ and SPPA that the cooperation is the only chacnce for us to stay in this market, discussing with CNPE DGM Zhong Hua was held in Erlanger in Oct. 2017. CNPE is requesting the IP transfering for the system which is belongs to DF, PG is not possible to make the decision. 2). agreed with FSP and HTC already, pilot project will be realized in FY18.  3). two technical roadshow haven been relized by HQ/SPPA/PD experts, Rayspower CSP is defined as must win project and customer shows strong intrests to Siemens technology.','2018-10-09 17:47:30','2018-10-09 17:47:30'),(33,33,'1) As a pilot, the CP control system modernization for CNPC is on pipeline together with CT. 2) Further communication with SGT FSP is under plan together with DG CN.','1) done.2) In progress, agreed with FSP and HTC already, pilot project will be realized in FY18.','2018-10-09 17:47:30','2018-10-09 17:47:30'),(34,34,'SU on localization of SST-600 in Huludao facilities','1. Joint business case between CP and SU is done. 2. The localization decision is done. The SST-600 EP is the product to be localized. 3. Localization team set-up in SU is done. And localization work is under preparation, real work is waiting for external orders. 4. 1st Project for standard SST-600 EP ASU received 5. Localization Kick Off Meeting held in SIT Huludao Oct 22-23, 2014 6. 1st Steering Committee to review Project Status 7. Localized Process & Interfaces established + RFQs/Quotations to Suppliers finished 8. New Project with Localized SST-600 EP ASU signed (2 Localized Steam turbines) 9. Project Execution is combined with Supplier / Product Qualification - in progress - 1st turbine will be delivered in July 2017.  10. 10th Steering Committee was held in Beijing in March and finalized SST-600 EP localization project.','2018-10-09 17:47:30','2018-10-09 17:47:30'),(35,35,'1. Set up DG technology footprint in China to benefit growth market in China1) DG hub in CT was established. The team includes application engineer and proposal engineer.Developing local sales force/proposal capacity to improve customer responsiveness and flexibility2) Set up local service competence, for I&C and O&M support.','1) A DG hub team of 20 people has been set up as of January 4th,2017, involved in Shan\'Xi Guoxin project and GCL(Golden Concord Holdings Limite, a power generation company in China) project, involved in project of ZNGT (Zhuzhou Nanfang Gas Turbine Corporation) SGT400  and HTC(Hangzhou Turbine Corporation) SGT800 package transfer and  localization project2) Contribution to marketing and sales:  completed 86 pre-acquisition requests, conducted 43 customer/Design institute interactions, organized 2 customer forums, supported 16 project bids3) Took the DG BU CEO intitive to build up customer support desk in China, it has been rolled out with 61 tickets closed4) Contribution to project execution: aligned and assigned engineering roles on control, mechanical and electrical modules, took the local sub-project manager role for GCL, Shanxi, Chengdu projects, conducted customer design liaison meetings and daily technical clarification with design institutes and partners, as well as on site support on installation and commissioning, supported warranty phase on urgent SGT-400 trip issues, supported Dongfang project on technical negotiation and order execution5) DG hub conducted the O&M(Operation and Manual)translation and check for Shanxi project with up to 24th batch, and for GCL with up to 18th batch6)Contribution to cost-out and procurement: took both core&package engineering and procurement role to support DTC(design to cost) work package of SGT-400 carrier ring, GVS(global value sourcing) on PPQ, technical clarification, vendor development and cost optimization, exhaust diffusor cost model generated and reviewed','2018-10-09 17:47:31','2018-10-09 17:47:31'),(36,36,'1) DG hub in CT was established. The team includes application engineer and proposal engineer.Developing local sales force/proposal capacity to improve customer responsiveness and flexibility2) Set up local service competence, for I&C and O&M support.','1)Ref Power Plant agreement signed with Jiangsu DI starting with SGT-800;  in planning of long term strategic cooperation. -- Ref Power Plant of SGT-800 is finished. Ref Power Plant of SGT-700 will start.2)Completed in Q2/2017.I&C and O&M teams set up. The competence is building up.','2018-10-09 17:47:31','2018-10-09 17:47:31'),(37,37,'Sign contract with DG customer (Zhongma)',' ','2018-10-09 17:47:31','2018-10-09 17:47:31'),(38,38,'Set up RAS digitalization practice in China.- Explore DIG opportunities with local customers','Won CR (Huarun) digitalization project','2018-10-09 17:47:31','2018-10-09 17:47:31'),(39,39,'Win at least 1 ST Mods contract in FY17 and 2 in FY18','In the final stage of negotiation with the customer','2018-10-09 17:47:31','2018-10-09 17:47:31'),(40,40,'(1) In-depth analysis of 13th 5YP, and Made in China 2025, and deriving proper conclusions for MO\'s business(2) Test acceptance of adjusted bidding approach (i.e. main contractor scoping) within MM MT and UT, reflecting easing and opening up of doing business in China in regards to Circular No. 5.','As to (1) reflected in China2020 strategy (i.e. upscaling volume for MM MT, UT MC, CS; downscaling MLT HI).As to (2): Three test cases for MM MT bids under preparation; in addition, revised approach as to Chestnut M&A project.In principle, opportunity through opening of rail market for multinational companies (State Council’s “circular No. 5”); so far some positive examples for a more fair treatment of foreign MNCs (i.e. signaling), but in general no clear guidance from the government as to the execution of concrete opening-up measures yet.','2018-10-09 17:47:31','2018-10-09 17:47:31'),(41,41,'Current 2 projects in MM, TGMT and Radio Communication, are in line with project schedule.','MM R&D Centre will be officially launched in Fuzhou in Q1/FY18.','2018-10-09 17:47:32','2018-10-09 17:47:32'),(42,42,'(1) Further increase of local added value scope of in-house suppliers, i.e. SMEC and SEDL, incl. redesign of components and their local sourcing.(2) Agreement of further local ramp up as to key resources (EN, R&D) in MLT and MM. (3) Stringent execution of established plans for collaborative component production in recently set up JVs (ZX: Motors for metros and High-speed; ZD: Gear boxes)','As to (1): Change in added value concept for TPE RE products agreed with SMEC. There is huge chance to further reduce SMEC price / cost due to change of key syppliers (e.g. GE to replace Secheron).As to (2): Respective plans part of BTA 2018; Ramp up of local HI team and at the same time ramp down SAG team to be partially agreed upon with 1st half year of FY18.As to (3): Alignment with ZH, PD LD and MO HQ on that in Q1/FY18.','2018-10-09 17:47:32','2018-10-09 17:47:32'),(43,43,'1. MLT: decision to design high speed locomotives offers us the opportunity to re-enter the locomotive market. 2. UT: portfolio expansion (2nd platform) to enlarge LRV market share.','1. There is aligned plan of capturing Locomotive orders in mainland China in place;2. this plan focusing on addressing a market niche which fits to our technical solution and is backed by partnership with Zongheng;3. With this approach we can address 10% Chinese Locomotive market in the mideum term;4. OI planned for FY18.','2018-10-09 17:47:33','2018-10-09 17:47:33'),(44,44,'MO: Regular alignment with HQ.UT: active promotion of our traction equipment to Chinese car builders for oversea market.MLT: Participating in mainline biddings in MLT in ASP and CIS.','(1)  LRT3 Malaysia booked in Sep.2017.(2) New Order for Iran metro likely to be booked in Q2/FY18. (Partnership with CRRC Puzhen)(3) OI pipeline (FY18): RMGL North Extension, RGSE ADD - both India ','2018-10-09 17:47:33','2018-10-09 17:47:33'),(45,45,'New Branch for battery business set up','Setting up is initiated. ','2018-10-09 17:47:34','2018-10-09 17:47:34'),(46,46,'New Sales&Marketing Organization for RAS in place, head located in Shanghai bundling all S&M activities','S&M head has already in place','2018-10-09 17:47:35','2018-10-09 17:47:35'),(47,47,'Mindsphere R&D centre set up in China ','R&D centre office is almost ready.Employee recruiting is on going.','2018-10-09 17:47:36','2018-10-09 17:47:36'),(48,48,'Investment Coorperation Agreement with CD government','Siemens and Chengdu Government singed Investment Coorperation Agreement in Aug. 2017.','2018-10-09 17:47:36','2018-10-09 17:47:36'),(49,49,'Capital Support by CD government','Government will provide capital support by subsidies to CDHT 3rd party customer who singed Industry 4.0 projects with Siemens. (About CNY 30m in total, 10% will benefit DF China). ','2018-10-09 17:47:36','2018-10-09 17:47:36'),(50,50,'Business License for R&D centre','Business License got. Formal set up date is Sep. 1st, 2017. ','2018-10-09 17:47:37','2018-10-09 17:47:37'),(51,51,'Investment Coorperation Agreement with CD government','Siemens and Chengdu Goverment singed Investment Coorperation Agreement in Aug. 2017.','2018-10-09 17:47:37','2018-10-09 17:47:37'),(52,52,'Capital support by CD government ','Government will provide capital support by subsidies to CDHT 3rd party customer who singed Industry 4.0 projects with Siemens. (About CNY 30m in total, 10% will benefit DF China) (80% of completion). ','2018-10-09 17:47:37','2018-10-09 17:47:37'),(53,53,'Joint Sales set up','on going','2018-10-09 17:47:37','2018-10-09 17:47:37'),(54,54,'Diligent (re-)evaluation of overdue allowances and judgments;Rigorous and regular tracking of defined measures;Escalation and involvement of MO HQ as to open technical topics if required; regular alignment with EY on the recoverability of AR positions.','(1) From Q2 to Q4 FY17, AR overdue position more than 90 days  could be reduced by 207\' RMB and 25% respectively. Therein, AR overdue position more than 360 days shows the lowest value since six quarters (down 17% in comparison to Q2/17)(2) As per October 1st, 2017, AR overdue position more than 90 days make 470\' RMB; nearly 50% of that is to be collected within the first half of FY18(3) Respective individual PMP targets will be passed on to BU and project managers in FY18 as well','2018-10-10 11:27:08','2018-10-10 11:27:08'),(55,55,'MS: SMVS & SSLS will be impacted',' ','2018-10-10 11:27:08','2018-10-10 11:27:08'),(56,56,'LP: SWAS will be impacted',' ','2018-10-10 11:27:08','2018-10-10 11:27:08'),(57,57,'a). Local partnership not only requires TOT and localization as in the past, but now also demand access to knowhow & IP (e.g. Shanghai Electric Group Company Ltd. (SEC)  & Ansaldo). Establish partnership with local company. Continounsly strengthen cooperation and partnership with HHI.b)Due to the tariff of gas and price of gas (short term), market is slow down. LGT/SGT will investigate in it. Regular review of the market forecast has been established.c) Tendency of electricity price cut will affect the market, PG S will keep close eye on the policy.','1)Ongoing measure. ToT agreement with HHI is being negotiated with HHI by GT BU. New partnership with Beizhong on F Class is being discussed. 2)Ongoing measure. Although the gas tariff is still an issue, but environmental pressure is driving the shut off of coal power plant and replacement by CHP. More ard more opportunities are identified and being followed by PG S.  3) Ongoing measure. Tendency of electricity tariff cut as well as lack of load will drive customer to low CAPEX and OPEX as much as possible. The cost reduction is being implemented by GT BU.','2018-10-10 11:27:08','2018-10-10 11:27:08'),(58,58,'PG ES: Negative impact to Turbine control System (TCS) and Digital Electronic Hydraulic (DEH) market share due to the change on local partnership of GT (SEC) in local market.Action:1) Strengthen collaboration and support to PG GT to defend local market share together by localization of TCS  2) focus on DRH units for DEH  3). Cooperate with FSP and HTC for SGT-800 TCS localization.','1)Ongoing measure. Project Won: RGE WuXi TCS project sold to SLC GT 2) Ongoing measure. Guodian Bengbu (Digital Electric Hydraulic Control System)DEH is awarded. Leizhou and Suqian are following.contracts are expected in Q1 FY18. 3) ongoing measure: agreed with FSP and HTC already, pilot project will be realized in FY18.','2018-10-10 11:27:08','2018-10-10 11:27:08'),(59,59,'PG DR : In areas of localization of manufacturing, procurement and adaptation to local needs, we have discrepancies comparing with our competitors. Steam Turbine Localization – DR compressors are sold with Steam Turbine as a package. Now in China, our competitor already has localized the steam turbine, we are far behind them, which lead to the high and uncompetitive compressor package price. As our customer could actually accept the localized solution, we have to speed up. Actions: 1) Enhance local engineering competence by setting up CT House and improve CT House oval capability; 2) Enhance local proposal competence in complete portfolio and all applications, such as transfer of ASU proposal from HQ to China. 3) More HQ transfer is expected, SITH owns the capability for GV-200 production, currently the local production / import parts is decided case by case during quotation phase, fully release for localization is expected. 4) Procurement team will re-evaluate existing suppliers as well as developing new suppliers, to enhance the quality and price strength from local suppliers5) workshop with Duisburg together with SU ( the steam turbine belongs to SU, but the risk lies in DR). Further develop SST-600 EP business case in Regional China and reach the Fiscal year order intake budget accordingly.','1. CT House team for DR China approved and installed.2. One ASU proposal expert from Duisburg delegated to Beijing. Trainings for proposals are on-going, esp. for legacy D-R products (e.g. Datum). 3. GV-200 localization in SITH was approved by Regionalization Board Meeting in Duisburg, and 1st loacaliztion project (Turpan_Xinrui_ASU_Domex, 1 x STC-GV(200-3)-- G - - STC-GV(20-5-H)) was awarded in FY15.Turpan project is still in implementation, with the compressor train delivered to the site and waiting for on-site installation and commissioning.4. \"Make of Buy\" scope was reviewed for all SITH portfolio and further supply base enhancement plan was incorporated in legacy CP China Growth Strategy (CP500) for implementation and will continue in the New DR China Growth Strategy. (DR China Procurement is working on developing Local for Global suppliers for legacy Dresser-Rand Olean plant on its components of hardware (紧固件) and  forge piece（锻件）). New supplier developed for gear box in Quzhou project (↓ 20% cost), for cooler in Sabalan project (↓ 28% cost), and for SST150 stator blades in Jindadi project (↓ 30% cost)5. Specific workshops on SST600 localization in China was held between DR Duisburge and SU in Germany, and  between DR China, SU China and SU HQ in Beijing China. Regular communication mechanism was set up. EP CN50/80 localization was approved, and three relevant projects were already awarded (Jingmen, Ordos Dalateqi, Wuyang-Hangyang) and in localization implementation. The extended type of localization was discussed and reviewed based on market demand monitoring in July and November meetings in 2016.  Further localization, cost-out and cycle time reduction measures are under consideration by SU HQ.Status Q4 FY 2016: 1st localization project (Jing